	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Sage>Slipskin</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>1092 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.25]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>At level 22 your are not in bad shape for weapons. Store bought instruments are about it at that level, too.&nbsp;&nbsp;Most instrument carrying MOBs are 30 plus in level.  <br><br>If you can get to Katta Kastellum on Luclin the bard instrument vendor sells Combine instruments which are about 10% better than regular instruments (based on what I read on EQDiva.com). <br><br>You don't say what your race is.  The Vah Shir Bards have a quest drum based off pottery skill.  It is not much but adds AC when equipped.  Eventually, the quest series leads to some really nice cloaks.<br><br>You don't say how much PP you have to spend or what kind of armor you are wearing.  Lambent armor can be bought from players but if you want to quest for it yourself you will need to wait awhile.  Some of the stuff needed requires a group in low 30's or even higher.<br><br></p>&nbsp;<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760</a></td></td></tr>
